(99, 1, '2016-01-20 23:35:33', '2016-01-20 23:35:33', 'WordPress is open-source technology, so no-one can monopolise it. That keeps competition high and prices low. Since we scale your website to you, you won’t have to pay for anything you don’t need.\r\n\r\n', 'It''s affordable.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'its-affordable', '', '', '2016-01-22 00:18:15', '2016-01-22 00:18:15', '', 121, 'http://localhost/wp-swiper/wordpress/?page_id=99', 1, 'page', '', 0),
